Tanzanian songstress Nandy has released 'Acha Lizame' featuring Harmonize. The song talks about two lovers who are showering praises to each other and are deeply in love and are ready to do everything it takes to keep their love and relationship going. Both Nandy and Harmonize say it was about time they gave their fans what they always asked for. They describe it as "a club banger with a dance vibe that can be played and danced to by anyone from across the world, despite the language". The audio was produced by Tanzanian producer Kimambo Beats and video directed by Elvis. 'Acha Lizame' is now trending on YouTube with over 1 million views.